      "description": "This F87 chassis M2 is powered by the N55 3.0L twin-scroll turbocharged inline-six, delivering a robust torque curve and exceptional throttle response. The powertrain is mated to a factory six-speed manual transmission featuring rev-matching technology for seamless downshifts. Mechanical highlights include the Active M Differential for optimized power distribution and lightweight aluminum suspension components derived from the M3/M4 for reduced unsprung mass. The vehicle exhibits tight steering rack feedback and precise turn-in, with the cooling system and bushings showing consistent maintenance. A mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s focused driver\u2019s coupe.",
